cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on improving the performance of convolutional networks on CIFAR and ImageNet, which are both computer vision tasks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes a new dropout method to deal with overfitting in neural networks, which is a common problem in machine learning. 
3. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper discusses the use of neural networks and proposes a new method to improve their performance. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new method to improve the performance of artificial neural networks. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - Although the paper focuses on computer vision tasks, it also mentions the use of natural language processing tasks, which falls under the scope of cs.CL.
